  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>DECORATE TO YOUR HEART'S CONTENT</strong></i><br>Immerse yourself in the Christmas spirit as you decorate to your heart’s content! Step into the role of a Christmas  designer, transforming plain trees into holiday masterpieces. Place each ornament and string up lights to create your very own Christmas tree</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/63cd20ae58dd33f9057369662803d7e8.poster.avif?t=1734997091\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/63cd20ae58dd33f9057369662803d7e8.webm?t=1734997091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/63cd20ae58dd33f9057369662803d7e8.mp4?t=1734997091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>FESTIVE CREATIVITY UNLEASHED</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax and let your imagination guide you—create themed trees and mix up your styles. Experiment with layers, patterns, and color schemes, and make each tree unique</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/1e5df9b474c7896c2702d9e02c0d596a.poster.avif?t=1734997091\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/1e5df9b474c7896c2702d9e02c0d596a.webm?t=1734997091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/1e5df9b474c7896c2702d9e02c0d596a.mp4?t=1734997091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>SPREAD HOLIDAY CHEER, ONE ORNAMENT AT A TIME</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are looking for a specific decoration and can't find it, you can make it. Use the detailed custom decoration maker to turn your ornament visions into reality. Share and download creations from the community on the Steam workshop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>DECORATE TO YOUR HEART'S CONTENT</strong></i><br>Immerse yourself in the Christmas spirit as you decorate to your heart’s content! Step into the role of a Christmas  designer, transforming plain trees into holiday masterpieces. Place each ornament and string up lights to create your very own Christmas tree</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/63cd20ae58dd33f9057369662803d7e8.poster.avif?t=1734997091\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/63cd20ae58dd33f9057369662803d7e8.webm?t=1734997091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/63cd20ae58dd33f9057369662803d7e8.mp4?t=1734997091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>FESTIVE CREATIVITY UNLEASHED</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax and let your imagination guide you—create themed trees and mix up your styles. Experiment with layers, patterns, and color schemes, and make each tree unique</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/1e5df9b474c7896c2702d9e02c0d596a.poster.avif?t=1734997091\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/1e5df9b474c7896c2702d9e02c0d596a.webm?t=1734997091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262860/extras/1e5df9b474c7896c2702d9e02c0d596a.mp4?t=1734997091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>SPREAD HOLIDAY CHEER, ONE ORNAMENT AT A TIME</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are looking for a specific decoration and can't find it, you can make it. Use the detailed custom decoration maker to turn your ornament visions into reality. Share and download creations from the community on the Steam workshop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
